* Calculates Cross-Country Team Scores
* When to use:      Use this when you need to generate a team standings report based on finishing places.


* How to use:       Ensure your CLUB (or team) field is populated. The script identifies the team field, sets the number of scoring members (default 5), 
*                   and the number of displacers (default 7).


*Alternative:       To score by total team time instead of finishing place, add the Team Score Time command to the script.
Header
.include            racename

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                          TEAM Results
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.End of Header
.include            fieldlst
Event               Finish
Team Field          CLUB
Team Score          5
Team Displace       7
 